data.description: Price reduction! Buyer will receive a home warranty for one year and a $1,000 towards closing cost at closing. LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!! This lovely 1,902 SqFt  one-story home has four bedrooms, two baths, and a wide-open layout; Has a NEW ROOF, New AC. Lots of space in every room with ceramic LUXURY tile throughout the entire house. The upgraded master bathroom offers a FANCY hotel-style shower with a water softer installed for the whole house and a cool barn door leading to the CONVENIENTLY with ORGANIZERS walk-in closet. The kitchen has a breakfast bar, a cozy nook, and a view of the dining and family areas. It also comes with a two-car garage. It's close to schools, a library, Posner Park Shopping Mall, and plenty of places to eat. Plus, easy access to I-4 in the direction of Walt Disney World, Downtown Disney, Sea World, Universal Studios, City Walk, Downtown Orlando, and the airport. Don't miss your opportunity to see this beautiful property, Schedule your appointment TODAY!
